bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY1mv0q.jpg&h=f5539593&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"010171800e65fa7e0b40eab50d40bf8304df1b96","tid":1364940,"uid":188421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b01b8baec46f6f86f7f0307d65c9ef0e9dd5db1","tid":1364940,"uid":289693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:35:35.000Z","msg":"如果真係Ringworm的話就咁local treatment 其實作用唔大因為ringworm d spores 已經會成身D毛同成屋環境都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 建議你去睇獸醫診斷係唔係ringworm 或者係其他原因<br />\n<br />\n你隻貓幾大? <br />\n之前有冇試過有咁甩毛情況?<br />\nindoor 定outdoor cat? <br />\n甩毛個位痕唔痕?  <br />\n屋企仲有冇其他寵物, 如果有咁佢地有冇同類症狀?<br />\n你身上有冇一D 好似下圖咁ge lesion/rash?<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wY1mv0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY1mv0q.jpg&h=f5539593&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:59:52.000Z","msg":"非常到位既問題 我認同要睇醫生 但暫時會買spray觀察兩日 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9-10個月大<br />\n甩毛最近既shedding season, 但局部我今次第一次見，但鑒於佢只係9-10月大，第一次見不能作準。<br />\n佢係strictly indoor cat<br />\n甩毛個位係腳底方向，所以好難判斷佢係groom定真係好痕，但我所見真係唔多去拗或者經想lam<br />\n<br />\n我無其他寵物，身上唔覺有症狀<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n最後，多謝咁有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Really appreciate it."},{"pid":"76daca56360f10af6e282c27ada814db5c6eb566","tid":1364940,"uid":188421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:44:06.000Z","msg":"本來打算買神仙水再觀察兩日，點知呢到係要醫生處方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53ee897a3fbeab2ac42e867e3019f3baa04df0f","tid":1364940,"uid":289693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"010171800e65fa7e0b40eab50d40bf8304df1b96","tid":1364940,"uid":188421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b01b8baec46f6f86f7f0307d65c9ef0e9dd5db1","tid":1364940,"uid":289693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:35:35.000Z","msg":"如果真係Ringworm的話就咁local treatment 其實作用唔大因為ringworm d spores 已經會成身D毛同成屋環境都有 <